Was just at a get together with co workers, and ofc politics was brought up, which led to an argument about the moon landing being fake...  I pointed out the reflector module that can still be used to verify a moon landing by using a high powered laser to reflect off it.  I was told that there is no light in space, and that was impossible. Stunned......  So I asked what they think light is?

The answer was "light comes from the sun".

I'm pulling out high school science, bringing up photons, in a basic ass way because I'm no goddamn scientist.  I was told that because I learned it in school it was therefore false and "that's what they want you to believe, because public school is mind control".

That fuckin photons are light particles?  There was 3 people screaming at me, telling me how wrong I was, and how I was being controlled by the government.

I was also referred to about 50 tiktok videos that had the "truth".  They were all some random person yelling about some bullshit, I questioned that, and was told I'm a sheep.

